snippet.title: Prehistoric Kingdom | Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/666150/Prehistoric_Kingdom/
Wishlist on Epic Games: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/prehistoric-kingdom

Take control of limitless power in Prehistoric Kingdom to build, manage and grow the ultimate zoo for extinct animals - arriving to Early Access April 27, 2022 for $29.99 USD.
